<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN293">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>niṟampaṭaik kolkā yāṉai mēlōṉ</l>
<l>kuṟumpark keṟiyu mēva ṟaṇṇumai</l>
<l>nāṇuṭai mākkaṭ kiraṅku māyi</l>
<l>ṉemmiṉum pēreḻi liḻantu viṉaiyeṉap</l>
<l>piṟarmaṉai pukuvaḷ kollō</l>
<l>vaḷiya ṭāṉē pūvilai peṇṭē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>When the Taṇṇumai drum sounds for the people ashamed [of showing weakness], </l>
<l>with the command to attack for those in the stronghold </l>
<l>of him on the elephant that does not yield to the weapon in [its] vital spot,</l>
<l>havng lost [her] gracefulness [once] greater than our’s, will she enter, </l>
<l>as [her] work, the house of another?</l>
<l>Pitiable she, woman with a price on flowers. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
